      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRINIT - Subroutine to do Program Initialisation.            *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By: Main Processing                                   *
      *                                                               *
      *  Calls    : None                                              *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRINIT    BEGSR
      *
      ** Set up copyright parameter
      *
     C                     MOVEACPY@      CPY2@  80
      *
      ***  Receive Parameter List.
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PSEQ    5
     C                     PARM           PENTY   3
      *
      ** Initialise LDA field.
      *
     C           *LOCK     IN   LDA
     C                     MOVEL'LE0301'  DBPGM
     C                     OUT  LDA
      *
      ** Read in Installation Data
      *
     C           *NAMVAR   DEFN           RUNDAT
     C           *NAMVAR   DEFN           LDA
     C                     IN   RUNDAT
      *
      ** Call Access Program for Bank Details
      *
     C           AGMBIN    IFEQ 'Y'
     C                     MOVE '1'       *IN37
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     CALL 'AOBANKR0'
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   PRTCD   7
     C                     PARM '*FIRST  'POPTN   7
     C           SDBANK    PARM SDBANK    DSFDY
      *
      ** Handle Database Error.
      *
     C           PRTCD     IFNE *BLANKS
     C           *LOCK     IN   LDA
     C                     MOVEL'SDBANKPD'DBFILE           ************
     C                     MOVEL'*FIRST  'DBKEY            * DBERR 01 *
     C                     Z-ADD1         DBASE            ************
     C                     OUT  LDA
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Check System Date Format, DDMMYY (*IN98 off)
      **                           MMDDYY (*IN98 on).
      *
     C           BJDFIN    IFEQ 'M'
     C                     MOVE '1'       *IN98
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE 'N'       WOPEN   1
     C                     Z-ADD0         WIFNO   50
     C                     Z-ADD0         WAFNO   50
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   WBRCA   3
     C                     Z-ADD*ZEROS    WFCTP   30
      *
      ** Define parameter list for AOBRCHR0
      *
     C           PPAR1     PLIST
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   PRTCD
     C                     PARM '*KEY   ' POPTN
     C                     PARM BRCA      PBRCH   3
     C           SDBRCH    PARM SDBRCH    DSSDY
      *
      ** Define parameter list for AOCURRR0
      *
     C           PPAR2     PLIST
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   PRTCD
     C                     PARM '*KEY   ' POPTN
     C                     PARM           PCURR   3
     C           SDCURR    PARM SDCURR    DSSDY
      *
      ** Define parameter list for AOFACTR0
      *
     C           PPAR3     PLIST
     C                     PARM '*BLANKS' PRTCD
     C                     PARM '*KEY   ' POPTN
     C                     PARM           PFACT   3
     C           SDFACT    PARM SDFACT    DSFDY
      *
      ** Define parameter list for AOCUSTR0
      *
     C           PPAR4     PLIST
     C                     PARM '*BLANKS' PRTCD
     C                     PARM '*KEY   ' POPTN
     C                     PARM           PKEYC  10
     C                     PARM           PKYSTS  7
     C           SDCUST    PARM SDCUST    DSSDY
      *
     C           WPMKY     KLIST
     C**********           KFLD           WPMFC   60                                          CSD027
     C                     KFLD           WPMFC   6                                           CSD027
     C                     KFLD           WPMFT   30
     C                     KFLD           WPMFN   20
